metadata.name: ETHRecord#1
metadata.description:
A story of somewhere not here.  
A story of a world that no human exists.  
A story of a world that is both the future and the past.  
It's a large basement in the small house where the paintings were found.  
We are perplexed because there are lots of paintings like no one has ever seen in this world.  
All of the paintings are square framed and have been very well preserved.    
The basement had many rooms and each of them were numbered.  
This painting was found in room 2, but we found only a picture frame in room 1.  
We are not sure what the things or the diagrams painted on it are.  
We searched the house high and low for records or documents about this painting, however could not find anything.  
We're so troubled that we decided to call this painting "#1".
